<font face="方正兰亭黑_GBK" size="47"><b><font face="方正准雅宋_GBK"></font></b></font><font size="45">黑仪 如果是这样的话</font>

236
00:13:15,100 --> 00:13:16,600
<font face="方正兰亭黑_GBK" size="47"><b><font face="方正准雅宋_GBK"></font></b></font><font size="45">那就不是「This is a pen.」</font>

237
